                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A former captain of the Royal Guard who ordered Halfdan and other guards to protect the people of Khaenri'ah at all costs.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Black Serpent Knights (Shadowy Husks)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Once upon a time, these were knights of the realm and carriers of significant status. The long years and a curse seem to have robbed them of their reason and memory. Now, all that remains within that armor is the will to \"fight for something, someone, and some matter.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Depending on how much wear and tear they have undergone, they are by turn known as \"Shadowy Husks\" or \"Black Serpent Knights.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
